Locations
United States

 






Alcoa’s U.S. portfolio includes four smelters, a refinery, hydroelectric power, a calcined coke plant and a spent potline treatment facility. Our Massena West smelter in New York State, established in 1902, is the longest continuously operating smelter in the world.




