alcoa inc/in
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Home & Office Products
Sub-Industry: Home Improvement
Alcoa Inc of Indiana provides fabricated aluminum products. The Company offers aerospace components, oil and gas drilling products, extrusions, as well as tubes.




